Section.name: About ASCET
Section.description:
Audisankara College of Engineering & Technology (ASCET) was established in the year 2001 by Dr. Penchalaiah Vanki, a notable academician. The college is affiliated JNTUA, Anantapur and approved by AICTE and NAAC with A Grade. It is also certified with ISO 9001-2000 and accredited with NBA. The college offers Undergraduate courses in Engineering and Postgraduate courses in Engineering, Computer and Business Administration.
